Beechat the first XMPP chat for Elgg
====================================

Beechat is a chat for Elgg using the XMPP protocol. It requires the XMPP server ejabberd and XML-RPC support.

$ sudo apt-get install ejabberd php5-xmlrpc


Installation
------------

